&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a motivated &lt;strong&gt;Contract Recruiter&lt;/strong&gt; to help fuel hiring at our rapidly growing SaaS company for the next few months (could extend) and up to 20-40 hours a week..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You&#39;re an experienced full-cycle recruiter who thrives in a fast-paced environment, loves connecting exceptional talent with meaningful opportunities, and embraces AI-powered recruiting tools to work smarter and deliver an outstanding candidate experience. You have hands-on full cycle recruiting experience with Greenhouse, enjoy partnering with hiring managers, and are always looking for innovative ways to identify, engage, and hire top talent.&lt;/p&gt;
