&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the full-cycle recruiting process from intake through offer acceptance for a variety of technical and business roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with hiring managers to develop recruiting strategies that align with business priorities and hiring goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively source exceptional talent across LinkedIn Recruiter, professional networks, referrals, and other sourcing channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI-powered recruiting tools to build talent pipelines, personalize candidate outreach, generate sourcing strategies, and improve recruiting efficiency while maintaining a human-first candidate experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use Greenhouse to manage candidates, ensure data integrity, and drive an organized, efficient hiring process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Screen and interview candidates, coordinate interview logistics, and guide candidates through each stage of the hiring process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build diverse, high-quality talent pipelines for current and future hiring needs.&lt;/li

